        TEX PLASTICS
    

Plastic Injection Moulding for UK OEMs
Our team are focused on helping you develop higher performing, lower cost solutions for your products.
Part of a financially sound and secure group, Tex Plastics operates from two UK locations. This provides a breadth of machine sizes and extensive in-house secondary operations - plus the highest levels of contingency.

Fast lead-time responses
Fast cycling machines
7/8 class cleanroom
White room and extensive added value

Our expertise in high-performance metal replacement materials is unrivalled, coupled with the most comprehensive service offering you will find. Because of this and our exceptional service levels - we are confident you will not get a better cost-value proposition anywhere else in the world.



Plastic Injection Moulding & Manufacturing Solutions
Looking for a plastic injection moulding supplier who will actively seek out ways to reduce your costs and increase your products' performance. Call Tex Plastics because our industry sector knowledge, expertise and lean processes will give you The Edge.
Buildings & Interiors • Construction & Exteriors • Electronics • Life Critical • Medical



